{"tid":1287750,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"練大隻！全部同我練大隻！（2)","createTime":"2019-07-05T10:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:04:38.000Z","uid":51801,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"71660bc50b73cde5ca89ebd3675150a4337a46da","tid":1287750,"uid":51801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"原post: <br />\n［長文慎入］ 練大隻！全部同我練大隻！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1280650/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1280650/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n前兩日開左post關於健身資訊發佈以及一對一mentorship programme，反應遠比想像中熱烈。好多新手想參加，亦有唔少尖撚巴絲甚至係專業健身教練想幫手做mentor，首先感謝大家支持！我地人手好少，而且有份正職，仲有好多巴絲我地未覆，請耐心等待。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有以下幾點想強調：<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 唔見面！唔見面！唔要見面！</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n如果你睇曬我地原post，仲問人住邊區咩邨，真係唔知懷唔懷疑你好。<br />\n講多次，我地暫時唔會考慮面對面指導／落區做運動。<br />\n一黎人手問題，二黎呢家風頭火勢，希望大家諒解。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>「遙距」</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地希望做到「遙距指導」，即係按你嘅目標，盡量分配一個技能／經驗相符嘅mentor比你，係唔需要見面嘅情況下，去幫你達到你嘅目標。我地嘅mentorship programme係由mentor因應mentee目標度身設計飲食同訓練餐單，以三個月為目標。我地相信只要你肯跟mentor嘅餐單堅持三個月，你會見到改變。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3.  「遙距」嘅缺點</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n下？遙距點樣執我嘅動作？相信好多人心入面都有呢個疑問。<br />\n我地嘅目標係帶起健身風氣，幫一班無從入手而卻步嘅新手由零開始。<br />\n我地希望幫呢班人踏出第一步，由完全唔做運動，去到至少會郁下，之後點樣發展，就睇下個人造化。<br />\n<br />\n你話執唔執到姿勢呢啲，我地認為網上有好多影片教學，十分詳細，你真係有心想改變嘅，一定有方法做到，甚至你拍低俾mentor 幫你執，都可以。你話一個人會無動力喎，一個人做運動好易放棄喎，一大班人做會有動力啲喎。記住，動力從來都係自己比自己，你唔想做，無人迫到你。<strong>我地只可以做到從旁協助，解答你疑難，幫你諗workout plan。我地唔可以代替你去做運動</strong>，希望大家可以體諒。<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得遙距幫你唔到，我地愛莫能助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為其實我地出post 前，都有幫唔少巴絲整plan。肯俾心機嘅，一個月已經開始體態有變化。<br />\n<br />\n4. [black]<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>保護自己私隱</ins></strong></span>[/black]<br />\n<br />\n上一個post有人擔心我地係鬼係狗，我地絕對明白呢個憂慮。得罪講句，我地仲驚過你。懇請大家係參與計劃過程中，千萬千萬唔好向我地透露任何過人資料。<br />\n聯絡我地嘅TG唔好用真相真名（見到有人TG用真相，我屌你咩）<br />\nfollow我地instgram之前set private，你唔嫌麻煩甚至可以另開太空account follow我地<br />\n同埋請唔好問我地健身以外嘅野，例如邊日去過邊做過乜。<br />\n<br />\n5. <strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">互相尊重</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地幾個冇諗過反應咁熱烈，覆咗兩晚都未覆晒，有部份巴絲等咗好耐，講起唔好意思先。<br />\n呢家整理緊數據，希望大家耐心等候。我地會進一步聯絡大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 聯絡方法<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到，如果大家對呢個遙距一對一嘅mentorship programme仍然有興趣，<br />\n（重複多次：不見面！不落區！不開班！）<br />\n歡迎係TG 聯絡我地 !<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><a href=\"http://t.me/fitness1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffitness1&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=70859188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/fitness1</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有健身疑問就可以係instgram DM 我地<br />\n我哋會定期分享健身相關資訊<br />\n我地係social media 上都係新手，有咩做得未夠好請多多見諒<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/easyfitness.easyfitness\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Feasyfitness.easyfitness&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=762e6ea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/easyfitness.easyfitness</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n（即係想參加計劃，牽涉到基本個人資料嘅，就用TG，純粹問問題，唔需要參加mentorship programme，就係IG呀！）"},{"pid":"e55859c48a8fa434d72c8e2a712e025805b2fc80","tid":1287750,"uid":2167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a842e40ec78f9008c47538a0a5a8075a0f6162","tid":1287750,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8faa9f326dfb0aa74353fe2cabef8041f175e8","tid":1287750,"uid":39495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:23:34.000Z","msg":"點練好啲心肺出去發夢？"},{"pid":"75cca76f71bbf911241480b78c1e9dc554646f30","tid":1287750,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:31:16.000Z","msg":"一齊練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb8ec9954ae1371135489945c15d6c2486d49b4","tid":1287750,"uid":51801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0f8faa9f326dfb0aa74353fe2cabef8041f175e8","tid":1287750,"uid":39495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:23:34.000Z","msg":"點練好啲心肺出去發夢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"比較推介hiit / 練耐力形式嘅阻力訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb335f487c147bd0f44af822fa76a9ff433a1104","tid":1287750,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9484340f56689f7471901cd4300c37799167c3d","tid":1287750,"uid":277296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:45:27.000Z","msg":"我無野講!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6dbdc6f46a299a84a6debc312f13b77133e9f6","tid":1287750,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a854e25a63bea6cef5dbb9dbcafd062d82851e","tid":1287750,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:05:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1334904f570b00002ebfd2f69d97e0f1b0a6e63","tid":1287750,"uid":274273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:06:36.000Z","msg":"借一借位<br />\n我係屍殺列車後一班車既乘客-有啲野想同今日無去遊行既人講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343942</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有咩理由反屋企都要我哋擔驚受怕（仲要有人跪地求饒，有大把人去完書展反屋企都被牽連），佢哋就逍遙法外，唔想驚到唔敢出街就幫手推！！！有野想講就歡迎補充，Plz！！！"},{"pid":"1ea5a83ead726995b8a9866724ec2ab9269f5799","tid":1287750,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:44:15.000Z","msg":"我宣布「政警鄉黑」大合作，「黑警、黑鄉、黑社會」合稱「三黑」，必須追究「三黑」暴行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1339336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1339336</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af7c2d1a9f4267493084726e10fd6d0b2cf0cec0","tid":1287750,"uid":68033,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:13:08.000Z","msg":"今日元朗 明日全港<br />\n全民健身 全民習武"},{"pid":"d203c480dac6e03d44b7c7a659c20a7e8ee42f86","tid":1287750,"uid":51801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d6dbdc6f46a299a84a6debc312f13b77133e9f6","tid":1287750,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d71c4dc52f3f551567a489255a77d96d362f4a","tid":1287750,"uid":107898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"支持，主流健身方法都要時間而未必見到成效而且需要一定知識去評估<br />\n小弟睇過本身《身體調教聖經》又譯《每週健身四小時》（The 4-hour Body) 裡面有提到一個快捷簡單既方法可以好快提升到體能，希望能幫到大家，當然呢個方法係一個入坑捷徑，希望大家多點了解運動既重要性<br />\n方法如下：<br />\n1:熱身:鑽跨(over under) 6-7下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YPqrauvIHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-YPqrauvIHg&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=79199a85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YPqrauvIHg</a><br />\n2:二擇其一:<br />\na:bench press 95-85% 1rm 2-3rep + plyo push up 4-5rep 為1set, 做2-3set, 每set之間休息5分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hqhkSm0v_9o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhqhkSm0v_9o&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=7b2b3ed1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hqhkSm0v_9o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QlsBDcMK9EY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQlsBDcMK9EY&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=2080f2db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QlsBDcMK9EY</a><br />\n或<br />\nb:push up 10-12rep<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IODxDxX7oi4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIODxDxX7oi4&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=ec40764a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IODxDxX7oi4</a><br />\n3:deadlift: 95-85% 1rm 2-3rep(拉到膝頭就放手掉/好快放低,不必拉晒全程亦唔好慢慢落) + 原地跳 5-7rep 為1set, 做2-3set, 每set之間休息5分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQgksUvFS1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXQgksUvFS1o&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=89fe3e3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQgksUvFS1o</a><br />\n4:torture twist:3-5set 3-5rep,每set之間休息30秒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_16Gp01zZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg_16Gp01zZM&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=36e68f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_16Gp01zZM</a><br />\n<br />\n目的:提升肌力<br />\n方法：高重量、低次數、低訓練量，還有淡化離心收縮訓練"},{"pid":"73317b1b78f9f1abc9178c50a3ee5d50a2b93bcd","tid":1287750,"uid":186808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:02:46.000Z","msg":"要係短時間內提升一般人嘅體能同內力，可以參考boot camp<br />\n最理想係唔需要equipment<br />\n隨時可以做<br />\n<br />\nburpees, push up, squat jump etc."},{"pid":"1fa3edee39d7c9b94650da63388e09567fb21c9c","tid":1287750,"uid":186808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"或者跟住消防體能要求，我諗佢哋係有用心設計過先訂立哩啲要求<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/source/recruit/training_guidebook_for_physical_fitness_test.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfsd.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fsource%2Frecruit%2Ftraining_guidebook_for_physical_fitness_test.pdf&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=bfde5823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/source/recruit/training_guidebook_for_physical_fitness_test.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"3d1e7d5f0067bd58e4da516bdaa94576709b4f67","tid":1287750,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d71c4dc52f3f551567a489255a77d96d362f4a","tid":1287750,"uid":107898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"支持，主流健身方法都要時間而未必見到成效而且需要一定知識去評估<br />\n小弟睇過本身《身體調教聖經》又譯《每週健身四小時》（The 4-hour Body) 裡面有提到一個快捷簡單既方法可以好快提升到體能，希望能幫到大家，當然呢個方法係一個入坑捷徑，希望大家多點了解運動既重要性<br />\n方法如下：<br />\n1:熱身:鑽跨(over under) 6-7下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YPqrauvIHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-YPqrauvIHg&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=79199a85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YPqrauvIHg</a><br />\n2:二擇其一:<br />\na:bench press 95-85% 1rm 2-3rep + plyo push up 4-5rep 為1set, 做2-3set, 每set之間休息5分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hqhkSm0v_9o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhqhkSm0v_9o&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=7b2b3ed1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hqhkSm0v_9o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QlsBDcMK9EY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQlsBDcMK9EY&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=2080f2db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QlsBDcMK9EY</a><br />\n或<br />\nb:push up 10-12rep<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IODxDxX7oi4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIODxDxX7oi4&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=ec40764a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IODxDxX7oi4</a><br />\n3:deadlift: 95-85% 1rm 2-3rep(拉到膝頭就放手掉/好快放低,不必拉晒全程亦唔好慢慢落) + 原地跳 5-7rep 為1set, 做2-3set, 每set之間休息5分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQgksUvFS1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXQgksUvFS1o&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=89fe3e3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQgksUvFS1o</a><br />\n4:torture twist:3-5set 3-5rep,每set之間休息30秒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_16Gp01zZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg_16Gp01zZM&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=36e68f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_16Gp01zZM</a><br />\n<br />\n目的:提升肌力<br />\n方法：高重量、低次數、低訓練量，還有淡化離心收縮訓練"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"呢個方法仲有個好處,係可以每日練"},{"pid":"cf7e557a37f32f44e58a6c3fd9b83569d4935ceb","tid":1287750,"uid":51801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"G 持<br />\n集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲想幫手<br />\n<br />\ntg 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2f5ce67cc1b94de4789d005a4ba9289a3a9a14","tid":1287750,"uid":51801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"［長文慎入］ 練大隻！全部同我練大隻！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280650\" data-auto-link targ